{"tid":755890,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"外匯牌價問題","createTime":"2018-07-25T14:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T14:39:01.000Z","uid":74530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a275684fdcf68d26ad1203219f5d4126d3514303","tid":755890,"uid":74530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:33:57.000Z","msg":"一般黎講, 外匯牌價都係分買入賣出兩種<br />\n買入 = 銀行買入, 賣出 = 銀行賣出<br />\n所以賣出價係一定會高過買入價<br />\n好似咁<br />\n例子: 恒生銀行<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/222659_fb5c81ed3a220004b71069645f112867.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F222659_fb5c81ed3a220004b71069645f112867.png&h=771e84a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但唯獨人民幣,<br />\n街邊找換店又好, 上網又好<br />\n多數都會見到佢個買入同賣出價係調轉<br />\n例子: 中銀, 許氏<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/222951_4a47a0db6e60853dedfcfdf08a5ca249.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F222951_4a47a0db6e60853dedfcfdf08a5ca249.png&h=230556e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/222955_fb5c81ed3a220004b71069645f112867.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F222955_fb5c81ed3a220004b71069645f112867.png&h=17dc2d13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我覺得依個設定完全係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , <br />\n如果d師奶啊婆唔識真係會好容易搞錯<br />\n定其實係有咩特別原因要咁做??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c587c0dd20e42dc685d995524d7b94013099b4b4","tid":755890,"uid":122537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc2826bcbdd4e8f262721d8382d53dd7a4ada33","tid":755890,"uid":74530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:39:01.000Z","msg":"奶野, 出錯圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n恒生:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/223854_10fb15c77258a991b0028080a64fb42d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F223854_10fb15c77258a991b0028080a64fb42d.png&h=1c958fa0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}